readable.content: A baseball player , a woman with Frisbees , and a dog in front of blue bleachers . A blonde haired girl is doing a trick with her dog that is in the air trying to catch a flying Frisbee . A dog jumping for a Frisbee while a woman crouches nearby . A woman thows a Frisbee to a dog as a baseball player in uniform runs behind her . The girl does freestyle Frisbee tricks with her dog at the baseball park .
